background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Monarch</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Reign</th><td>\n~ Beginning during the <a href=\"/index.php/Century_of_Blood\" title=\"Century of Blood\">Century of Blood</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Full name</th><td>\nArrec Durrandon</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Storm_King\" title=\"Storm King\">Storm King</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Heir</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Arlan_V_Durrandon\" title=\"Arlan V Durrandon\">Arlan V Durrandon</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Successor</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Arlan_V_Durrandon\" title=\"Arlan V Durrandon\">Arlan V Durrandon</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Family</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Dynasty</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Durrandon\" title=\"House Durrandon\">House Durrandon</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Arlan_V_Durrandon\" title=\"Arlan V Durrandon\">Arlan V Durrandon</a><br />Son(s)</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">References</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i> (appendix)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Arrec Durrandon</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Storm_King\" title=\"Storm King\">Storm King</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">stormlands</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Durrandon\" title=\"House Durrandon\">House Durrandon</a> who lost the wealthy <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a> to the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Islands\" title=\"Iron Islands\">Iron Islands</a>. He was also the grandsire of the last Storm King, <a href=\"/index.php/Argilac_Durrandon\" title=\"Argilac Durrandon\">Argilac Durrandon</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_reign_of_the_dragons:_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_reign_of_the_dragons:_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Arrec_Durrandon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Arrec was the last Storm King to rule the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a>, an area conquered by his ancestor <a href=\"/index.php/Arlan_III_Durrandon\" title=\"Arlan III Durrandon\">Arlan III Durrandon</a> some three hundred years earlier. <a href=\"/index.php/Harwyn_Hoare\" title=\"Harwyn Hoare\">Harwyn Hardhand</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Iron_Islands\" title=\"King of the Iron Islands\">King of the Iron Islands</a>, used the mobility of <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a> longships to defeat the stormlanders in the riverlands. Arrec's greatest defeat was in the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_at_Fairmarket\" title=\"Battle at Fairmarket\">Battle at Fairmarket</a>. Later in life, Arrec tried twice to cross the <a href=\"/index.php/Blackwater_Rush\" title=\"Blackwater Rush\">Blackwater</a> and take back the lost lands, but failed.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> Arrec was succeeded by his eldest son, <a href=\"/index.php/Arlan_V_Durrandon\" title=\"Arlan V Durrandon\">Arlan V</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Arrec_Durrandon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td><div style=\"width:1em; height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:1em; height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black;\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black;\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black;\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px s